Package: deltasharingr
Title: Delta Sharing Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Developer", "Name", email = "developer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R client for the Delta Sharing protocol, enabling secure data
    sharing across organizations. Provides functions to connect to Delta Sharing
    servers, list shares, schemas, and tables, and read shared data into R.
